	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As Rainwarrior said, QR codes are in practice a tool to solve the problem that phone keyboards are terrible. Outside of that context ... mostly they just feel obfuscatory.<br /><br /><span style="font-size: 50%; line-height: normal">(<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QR_code" class="postlink">Wikipedia can tell you more than you actually want to know</a> about QR codes, what they can hold, and how they work.)</span>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


